title: T.I Interview and More
itunes:title: T.I Interview and More
description:
Thursday 10/3- Today on the show we had future Florida Governor Andrew Gillum stop by, where he gave us the updates on his campaign and more. Also, we had king of the south T.I pull up on us, where he spoke about his new album, curating trap music, and did you know he skipped out on signing Drake? Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to yet another Florida Man who tried to buy someone's daughter at Walmart and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
